<h2 id="20">2. Converting currencies</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <a href="/en/item/managing-items#870"><strong>Setup Â» Item Â» Sales prices</strong></a> and activate the option <strong>Currency: Live conversion</strong> to determine if the currency conversion in the online store is carried out automatically.<br>
In addition, carry out general currency settings for all incoming orders in the menu <strong>Setup Â» Orders Â» Payment Â» Currencies</strong>. To do so, proceed as described below.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
