<td class="content">
<div class="title">Replacing currency symbols</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you previously worked with currency symbols, replace them with the template variable <strong>$Currency</strong>. The template variable <strong>$Currency</strong> always contains the currency that is currently selected in the online store.</p>
</div>
